OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire and Rescue team
OL,4,Crecognised for 'heroic' earthquake
OL,5,Crescue work
OL,7,FThe acting President of Venezuela,
OL,8,FDelcy Rodriguez, has honoured a team
OL,9,Ffrom South Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,10,FService with "Hero of Venezuela"
OL,11,Fmedals.
OL,13,FThe honours, which recognise
OL,14,F"dedication and heroism", were
OL,15,Fpresented to international rescuers
OL,16,Fwho volunteered with UK ISAR in
OL,17,Fresponse to the devastating
OL,18,Fearthquakes.
OL,26,@rD@NOUrD@`O]vD@AOUvD@XO]
