OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783676987
OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire and Rescue team
OL,4,Crecognised for 'heroic' earthquake
OL,5,Crescue work
OL,7,FSix members of SWFRS used their
OL,8,Fspecialist skills to support the
OL,9,Frescue phase of the operation, as part
OL,10,Fof a contingent from 14 of the UK's
OL,11,Ffire services.
OL,13,FThe UK ISAR deputy team leader was
OL,14,FSWFRS's Group Manager Darren Cleaves,
OL,15,Fwho was overseeing the command and
OL,16,Fcoordination of assets and resources
OL,17,Fon the ground.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
