PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783676987
OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire and Rescue team
OL,4,Crecognised for 'heroic' earthquake
OL,5,Crescue work
OL,7,FGroup Manager Cleaves was presented
OL,8,Fwith the Venezuelan nation's highest
OL,9,Frecognition for "dedication, nobility
OL,10,Fand heroism of those who, defying all
OL,11,Fdifficulties, devote their work to
OL,12,Fhumanitarian assistance and aid."
OL,14,FGM Cleaves said: "I was incredibly
OL,15,Fproud to deploy alongside five
OL,16,Fcolleagues from South Wales Fire and
OL,17,FRescue Service.
OL,26,@qD@QOUtD@aO]vD@ROU
