OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire and Rescue team
OL,4,Crecognised for 'heroic' earthquake
OL,5,Crescue work
OL,7,F"Despite the heartbreak, we also
OL,8,Fwitnessed the very best of humanity.
OL,9,FCommunities supporting one another
OL,10,Fthrough unimaginable circumstances and
OL,11,Femergency responders from around the
OL,12,Fworld working side by side with one
OL,13,Fshared purpose ` to save lives,
OL,14,Fprovide hope and stand with those who
OL,15,Fneed us most."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@NO]
