OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire and Rescue team
OL,4,Crecognised for 'heroic' earthquake
OL,5,Crescue work
OL,7,FSupporting GM Cleaves in the mission
OL,8,Fwere Kev Dite, Tristan Bowen, Robert
OL,9,FBuckley, Luke Davies and Adrian
OL,10,FCummings, all of whom have extensive
OL,11,Fexperience in international rescue
OL,12,Foperations, including specialist
OL,13,Fcapabilities in shoring, breaching,
OL,14,Fand breaking ` all critical to
OL,15,Flocating and accessing casualties
OL,16,Ftrapped within collapsed structures.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
