CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783676987
OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire and Rescue team
OL,4,Crecognised for 'heroic' earthquake
OL,5,Crescue work
OL,7,FThe Service has supported ISAR
OL,8,Ftraining and deployments for more than
OL,9,F25 years and the UK ISAR team was
OL,10,Fdeployed through the Foreign,
OL,11,FCommonwealth & Development Office,
OL,12,Ffollowing a request for support from
OL,13,Fthe Venezuelan government.
OL,15,FThe team from SWFRS is now safely home
OL,16,Fand have thanked the Service, their
OL,17,Fcolleagues, and especially their
OL,18,Ffamilies and friends for all the
OL,19,Fsupport they've received.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/6
